%20a%20say%20in%20the%20matter%20and%20stated%20he%20has%20%E2%80%98no%20idea'%20when%20the%20legendary%20player%20will%20consider%20hanging%20up%20his%20boots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNo%2C%20that's%20not%20my%20role%20to%20put%20an%20end%20to%20it.%20I%20have%20no%20idea.%20I'm%20just%20enjoying%20working%20with%20him%20still.%20He's%20still%20going%20strong.%20I%20don't%20even%20ask%20these%20days.%20You%20are%20the%20ones%20who%20ask%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Fleming%20in%20the%20post-game%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743995280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fa1lfmsb_ms-dhoni-bcci_625x300_06_April_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2025%2Fms-dhoni-sent-brutal-message-by-pakistan-great-amid-ipl-2025-struggle-shouldve-left-long-back-8101500%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Once%20labelled%20as%20the%20finisher'%20in%20Indian%20cricket%2C%20MS%20Dhoni%20is%20under%20serious%20pressure%20after%20failing%20to%20contribute%20to%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings'%20run%20chase%20for%20a%20third%20straight%20game%20in%20the%20IPL%202025%20season.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2025%2Fms-dhoni-sent-brutal-message-by-pakistan-great-amid-ipl-2025-struggle-shouldve-left-long-back-8101500%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hrithik%20calls%20Jr%20NTR%20'best%20chef%20in%20the%20world'-%20WATCH%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743995192000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-120051227%2Cimgsize-14118.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fhrithik-roshan-calls-jr-ntr-best-chef-in-the-world-hails-war-2-actor-as-his-favourite-co-star-watch%2Farticleshow%2F120050968.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%