my%20bowling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20professional%2C%20when%20you%20are%20consistently%20with%20the%20Indian%20team%2C%20a%20doubt%20grows%20in%20your%20mind%20(on%20him%20being%20dropped)%20but%20I%20cheered%20myself%20up%20and%20was%20looking%20forward%20to%20the%20IPL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20execute%20what%20you%20are%20trying%20to%20deliver%2C%20you%20stay%20at%20the%20top.%20When%20you%20move%20the%20ball%20both%20in%20and%20out%20and%20it%20works%20instinctively%2C%20it%20gives%20you%20a%20different%20feeling.%26quot%3B%20Siraj%20was%20delighted%20that%20he%20could%20perform%20so%20well%20with%20his%20parents%20watching%20him%20from%20the%20stands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20come%20to%20your%20home%20ground%2C%20it's%20a%20special%20feeling.%20My%20family%20was%20there%20in%20the%20crowd%20and%20that%20lifted%20me%20up.%20I%20have%20played%20seven%20years%20for%20RCB.%20I%20have%20worked%20hard%20on%20my%20bowling%20and%20also%20on%20my%20mindset%2C%20it's%20working%20really%20well%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Siraj%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBowling%20first%2C%20GT%20restricted%20SRH%20to%20152%20for%20eight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGill%20praises%20bowlers%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGujarat%20Titans%20skipper%20Shubman%20Gill%20lavished%20praise%20on%20his%20bowlers%20after%20their%20comfortable%20victory%20over%20hosts%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad%2C%20terming%20them%20%26quot%3Bgame-changers%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20shortest%20format.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBowlers%20are%20game-changers%2C%20especially%20in%20this%20format.%20Lot%20of%20people%20talk%20about%20T20s%2C%20batting%20and%20hitting%2C%20but%20we%20think%20matches%20are%20won%20by%20bowlers%20and%20that%20is%20why%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20emphasis%20on%20bowlers%20(in%20this%20franchise).%26quot%3B%20Gill%20led%20from%20the%20front%20with%20the%20bat%2C%20remaining%20not%20out%20on%2061%20off%2043%20balls.%20The%20skipper%20was%20also%20pleased%20to%20see%20the%20talented%20Washington%20Sundar%20excelling%20on%20GT%20debut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20(Washington)%20was%20very%20close%20(to%20playing)%20in%20the%20game%20against%20Mumbai.%20He%20was%20padded%20the%20whole%20game%2C%20but%20with%20the%20impact%20player%20rule%2C%20it%20gives%20you%20an%20opportunity%20to%20play%20someone%20else%20(if%20you%20need%20an%20extra%20bowler)%2C%26quot%3B%20Gill%20said%20of%20Washington.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20all%20about%20having%20a%20good%20partnership%2C%20and%20we%20said%20once%20we%20are%20set%2C%20we%20will%20take%20it%20from%20there.%26quot%3B%20About%20Siraj%2C%20Gill%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20energy%20he%20brings%20is%20tremendous.%20When%20playing%20against%20him%2C%20you%20want%20him%20in%20your%20team.%20His%20energy%20is%20infectious.%26quot%3B%20On%20his%20part%2C%20Washington%20said%20the%20advice%20from%20his%20captain%20was%20to%20take%20the%20game%20deep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSkipper%20kept%20telling%20me%20to%20play%20as%20deep%20as%20possible.%20Got%20off%20to%20a%20good%20start%20and%20wanted%20to%20bat%20as%20deep%20as%20possible%20and%20finish%20for%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20has%20been%20the%20trend%20in%20Hyderabad%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years.%20In%20the%20second%20innings%2C%20the%20wicket%20gets%20better%20and%20easier%20to%20chase%20160-170%20on%20the%20board.%20I%20was%20well%20aware%20of%20it%20and%20it%20helped%20me.%26quot%3B%20SRH%20skipper%20Pat%20Cummins%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNot%20a%20traditional%20Hyderabad%20wicket%2C%20tough%20to%20get%20fluency%20in%20your%20innings.%20At%20the%20end%20there%2C%20it%20did%20not%20spin%20as%20much%20as%20we%20thought.%20A%20few%20(runs)%20short%20and%20they%20batted%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743991800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fjua7cbe_sc_625x300_06_April_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2025%2Fwasnt-able-to-digest-mohammed-sirajs-brutally-honest-revelation-on-champions-trophy-2025-snub-8103150%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pacer%20Mohammed%20Siraj%20on%20Sunday%20said%20he%20was%20initially%20struggling%20to%20come%20to%20terms%20after%20being%20dropped%20from%20the%20Indian%20team%20for%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20earlier%20this%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2025%2Fwasnt-able-to-digest-mohammed-sirajs-brutally-honest-revelation-on-champions-trophy-2025-snub-8103150%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mega%20Plunge%20In%20Asian%20Markets%2C%20US%20Futures%20Down%20In%20Big%20Trump%20Tariff%20Fallout%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAsian%20markets%20took%20a%20huge%20plunge%20Monday%20as%20US%20futures%20pointed%20to%20significant%20losses%20on%20Wall%20Street%20over%20Donald%20Trump's%20punishing%20tariffs%2C%20even%20as%20countries%20sought%20compromise%20with%20the%20defiant%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20denied%20Sunday%20he%20was%20intentionally%20engineering%20a%20selloff%20and%20insisted%20he%20could%20not%20foresee%20market%20reactions%2C%20saying%20he%20would%20not%20make%20a%20deal%20with%20other%20countries%20unless%20trade%20deficits%20were%20solved.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSometimes%20you%20have%20to%20take%20medicine%20to%20fix%20something%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20the%20market%20pain%20that%20has%20seen%20trillions%20of%20dollars%20wiped%20off%20the%20value%20of%20US%20companies%20since%20the%20beginning%20of%20his%20tariff%20rampage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20aboard%20Air%20Force%20One%2C%20he%20added%20that%20he%20had%20sought%20to%20resolve%20the%20issue%20with%20world%20leaders%20over%20the%20weekend%2C%20claiming%20%26quot%3Bthey're%20dying%20to%20make%20a%20deal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20retaliated%20against%20the%20United%20States%20on%20Friday%2C%20announcing%20it%20would%20impose%20tit-for-tat%20tariffs%20of%2034%20percent%20on%20all%20US%20goods%20from%20April%2010%20after%20Asian%20markets%20closed%20last%20week.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20trade%20war%20escalating%2C%20stocks%20in%20Asia%20took%20a%20heavy%20hammering%20when%20trading%20resumed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20early%20trade%20on%20Monday%20in%20Japan%20the%20Nikkei%20225%20was%20off%20an%20eye-watering%206.5%20percent%2C%20while%20stocks%20in%20Taiwan%20were%20down%20almost%2010%20percent%20and%20in%20Singapore%208.5%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFutures%20contracts%20for%20the%20New%20York%20Stock%20Exchange's%20main%20boards%20were%20sharply%20down%20Sunday%2C%20suggesting%20more%20pain%20for%20battered%20Wall%20Street%20stocks%20when%20markets%20open%20Monday%2C%20while%20US%20oil%20dropped%20below%20%2460%20a%20barrel%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%20April%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Deals%20And%20Alliances'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBenjamin%20Netanyahu%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20of%20Israel%20--%20which%20has%20been%20hit%20with%2017%20percent%20tariffs%2C%20despite%20being%20one%20of%20Washington's%20closest%20allies%20--%20will%20fly%20in%20for%20crunch%20talks%20with%20Trump%20Monday%20on%20the%20levies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBritain's%20Prime%20Minister%20Keir%20Starmer%20warned%20in%20a%20newspaper%20op-ed%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20world%20as%20we%20knew%20it%20has%20gone%2C%26quot%3B%20saying%20the%20status%20quo%20would%20increasingly%20hinge%20on%20%26quot%3Bdeals%20and%20alliances.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20staggered%20deadlines%20have%20left%20space%20for%20some%20countries%20to%20negotiate%2C%20even%20as%20he%20insisted%20he%20would%20stand%20firm%20and%20his%20administration%20warned%20against%20any%20retaliation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMore%20than%2050%20countries%20have%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20president%20to%20begin%20a%20negotiation%2C%26quot%3B%20Kevin%20Hassett%2C%20head%20of%20the%20White%20House%20National%20Economic%20Council%2C%20told%20ABC's%20This%20Week%20on%20Sunday%2C%20citing%20the%20US%20Trade%20Representative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVietnam%2C%20a%20manufacturing%20powerhouse%20that%20counted%20the%20US%20as%20its%20biggest%20export%20market%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%2C%20has%20already%20reached%20out%20and%20requested%20a%20delay%20of%20at%20least%2045%20days%20to%20thumping%2046%20percent%20tariffs%20imposed%20by%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHassett%20said%20countries%20seeking%20compromise%20were%20doing%20so%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20they%20understand%20that%20they%20bear%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20tariffs%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20the%20administration%20continues%20to%20insist%20that%20the%20duties%20would%20not%20lead%20to%20major%20price%20rises%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20that%20you're%20going%20to%20see%20a%20big%20effect%20on%20the%20consumer%20in%20the%20US%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Markets%20Bloodbath'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETreasury%20Secretary%20Scott%20Bessent%20also%20told%20NBC's%20Meet%20the%20Press%20that%2050%20countries%20had%20reached%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20for%20whether%20Trump%20will%20negotiate%20with%20them%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20that's%20a%20decision%20for%20President%20Trump%2C%26quot%3B%20Bessent%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20this%20moment%20he's%20created%20maximum%20leverage%20for%20himself...%20I%20think%20we're%20going%20to%20have%20to%20see%20what%20the%20countries%20offer%2C%20and%20whether%20it's%20believable%2C%26quot%3B%20Bessent%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20countries%20have%20been%20%26quot%3Bbad%20actors%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20and%20it's%20not%20the%20kind%20of%20thing%20you%20can%20negotiate%20away%20in%20days%20or%20weeks%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20hopes%20for%20negotiations%20to%20avert%20the%20worst%20economic%20carnage%2C%20in%20Asia%20the%20markets%20bloodbath%20continued%20into%20the%20new%20trading%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20where%20the%20markets%20were%20open%20Sunday%2C%20the%20bourse%20was%20down%206.78%20percent%20--%20the%20worst%20daily%20loss%20since%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic%2C%20according%20to%20state%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELarry%20Summers%2C%20formerly%20Director%20of%20the%20National%20Economic%20Council%20under%20president%20Barack%20Obama%2C%20said%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20a%20very%20good%20chance%20there's%20going%20to%20be%20more%20turbulence%20in%20markets%20the%20way%20we%20saw%20on%20Thursday%20and%20Friday.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeter%20Navarro%2C%20Trump's%20tariff%20guru%2C%20has%20pushed%20back%20against%20the%20mounting%20nervousness%20and%20insisted%20to%20investors%20that%20%26quot%3Byou%20can't%20lose%20money%20unless%20you%20sell%2C%26quot%3B%20promising%20%26quot%3Bthe%20biggest%20boom%20in%20the%20stock%20market%20we've%20ever%20seen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%20has%20not%20been%20targeted%20by%20the%20latest%20raft%20of%20tariffs%2C%20and%20Hassett%20cited%20talks%20with%20Moscow%20over%20its%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%20as%20the%20reason%20for%20their%20omission%20from%20the%20hit%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%20a%20White%20House%20official%20suggested%20the%20reason%20for%20Russia's%20omission%20was%20because%20trade%20was%20negligible%20thanks%20to%20sanctions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20long%20insisted%20that%20countries%20around%20the%20world%20that%20sell%20products%20to%20the%20United%20States%20are%20in%20fact%20ripping%20Americans%20off%2C%20and%20he%20sees%20tariffs%20as%20a%20means%20to%20rig