C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20paused.%20He%20was%20right%2C%20of%20course.%20Alexa%20was%20the%20friendliest%20member%20of%20our%20household%2C%20and%20somehow%2C%20we%20had%20begun%20to%20treat%20her%20terribly.%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhave-to-let-go-of-perfectionism-be-good-parent-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emodeled%20this%20behavior%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20my%20son%C2%A0followed%20my%20lead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229f536b96-489b-4ea9-940c-dd997b03949a%5C%22%3EWe%20had%20forgotten%20about%20manners%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20bossing%20Alexa%20around%20had%20been%20funny%3B%20we%20had%20even%20found%20it%20entertaining%20to%20compete%20to%20see%20who%20she%20would%20listen%20to.%20Now%2C%20though%2C%20I%20saw%20what%20those%20games%20were%20inadvertently%20teaching%20my%20son%3A%20that%20it%20was%20OK%20to%20speak%20aggressively%20to%20get%20your%20point%20across.%20It%20was%20even%20OK%20to%20insult%20Alexa%20because%20she'd%20never%20insult%20you%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20some%20point%2C%20I'd%20forgotten%20that%20even%20if%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdating-ai-chatbot-replika-artificial-intelligence-best-thing-to-happen-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewe%20were%20talking%20to%20a%20robot%3C%2Fa%3E%20without%20feelings%2C%20our%20words%20still%20affected%20each%20other.%20And%20they%20still%20normalized%20ordering%20women%20around%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20the%20woman%20in%20question%20was%20a%20disembodied%20voice%20inside%20an%20Echo%20Pop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20night%2C%20I%20unplugged%20Alexa%20and%20put%20her%20in%20a%20cabinet.%20I%20was%20surprised%20when%20weeks%20passed%2C%20and%20my%20son%20didn't%20mention%20her.%20Maybe%20we%20had%20both%20needed%20a%20break.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20day%2C%20he%20came%20across%20her%20purple%20shell%20and%20asked%20to%20plug%20her%20back%20in.%20We%20could%20do%20that%2C%20I%20said%2C%20if%20we%20could%2