adu's%20Pamban%20bridge%20today%2C%20mocked%20the%20Opposition%2C%20saying%20they%20are%20like%20people%20who%20cry%20without%20any%20reason.%20In%20the%20backdrop%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20MK%20Stalin's%20complaints%20about%20delimitation%20and%20the%20third%20language%20issue%2C%20PM%20Modi%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20funds%20allocated%20for%20the%20rail%20projects%20of%20the%20state%20has%20gone%20up%20nearly%20seven%20times.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20infrastructure%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20is%20a%20top%20priority%20for%20the%20government...%20Before%202014%2C%20only%20Rs%20900%20crore%20were%20received%20every%20year%20for%20rail%20projects%20and%20you%20all%20know%20who%20was%20heading%20the%20INDI%20Alliance%20at%20that%20time.%20This%20time%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20rail%20budget%20is%20more%20than%20Rs%206000%20crore%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20amid%20allegations%20of%20inadequate%20allocation%20of%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20is%20also%20modernising%2077%20railway%20stations%2C%20including%20the%20one%20in%20Rameswaram%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20to%20the%20Centre's%20largesse%20in%20another%20area%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOver%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20under%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Gram%20Sadak%20Yojana%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20work%20has%20been%20done%20on%20village%20roads%20and%20highways%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%202014%2C%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20central%20government%2C%20around%204%2C000%20km%20of%20roads%20have%20been%20built%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Stalin%20has%20repeatedly%20alleged%20that%20the%20Centre%20has%20been%20attempting%20to%20curb%20the%20southern%20states%20-%20politically%20through%20delimitation%20and%20culturally%20through%20the%20three-language%20policy.%20The%20Centre%2C%20he%20said%2C%20has%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20the%20state's%20funds%20will%20be%20held%20back%20if%20it%20did%20not