l%20engineer%20who%20came%20to%20NID%20to%20study%20design%20for%20agriculture%20%E2%80%94%20and%20after%20graduation%20in%201986%2C%20moved%20to%20Udaipur.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20373px)%20100vw%2C%20373px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FDr-Lakshmi-with-Dr-Kailash-Brijwasi-director-of-Jatan-Sansthan_11zon-1743518841.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22373%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Co-founders%20of%20Jatan%20Sansthan%2C%20Lakshmi%20and%20Dr%20Kailash%20have%20trained%20thousands%20in%20menstrual%20health%20and%20grassroots%20innovation.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FDr-Lakshmi-with-Dr-Kailash-Brijwasi-director-of-Jatan-Sansthan_11zon-1743518841.jpg%20373w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FDr-Lakshmi-with-Dr-Kailash-Brijwasi-director-of-Jatan-Sansthan_11zon-1743518841-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FDr-Lakshmi-with-Dr-Kailash-Brijwasi-director-of-Jatan-Sansthan_11zon-1743518841-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FDr-Lakshmi-with-Dr-Kailash-Brijwasi-director-of-Jatan-Sansthan_11zon-1743518841-200x200.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FDr-Lakshmi-with-Dr-Kailash-Brijwasi-director-of-Jatan-Sansthan_11zon-1743518841-96x96.jpg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-417316%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22373%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECo-founders%20of%20Jatan%20Sansthan%2C%20Lakshmi%20and%20Dr%20Kailash%20have%20trained%20thousands%20in%20menstrual%20health%20and%20grassroots%20innovation.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20many%20challenges.%20Connectivity%20was%20poor%20%E2%80%94%20we%20only%20had%20metre%20gauge%20trains%20to%20Ahmedabad%20and%20Delhi%2C%20and%20just%20one%20flight%20to%20Mumbai%20and%20one%20to%20Delhi.%20Apart%20from%20that%2C%20there%20was%20the%20prevalent%20patriarchy.%20People%20called%20me%20%3Cem%3Ebhabhiji%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Edidi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20or%20Lakshmiji.%20They%20didn%E2%80%99t%20understand%20my%20work.%20My%20attire%20was%20very%20different%20from%20the%20locals.%20I%20wore%20trousers%20and%20shirts%20in%20a%20place%20where%20women%20wore%20%3Cem%3Esaris%3C%2Fem%3E%20with%20%3Cem%3Egoonghats%20%3C%2Fem%3E(veils)%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20liberal%20in-laws%2C%20especially%20her%20mother-in-law%2C%20who%20worked%20in%20education%2C%20were%20a%20blessing.%20But%20the%20lack%20of%20ceramic%20design%20opportunities%20in%20Udaipur%20meant%20she%20had%20to%20carve%20a%20new%20path.%20She%20began%20organising%20artist%20camps%2C%20helping%20potters%20and%20artisans%20create%20new%20products%2C%20and%20soon%20started%20working%20with%20the%20NGO%20Seva%20Mandir%2C%20designing%20visual%20communication%20tools%20for%20rural%20communities.%20%E2%80%9CI%20could%20have%20moved%20back%20to%20Ahmedabad%20and%20pursued%20ceramics%2C%20but%20at%20the%20time%2C%20having%20a%20long-distance%20marriage%20just%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20considered%20acceptable%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESketching%20periods%20into%20the%20picture%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELakshmi%E2%80%99s%20first%20real%20brush%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F246267%2Fmenstrual-hygiene-kit-cloth-pads-avni-safepads-women-health-ana79%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emenstrual%20health%20%3C%2Fa%3Ecame%20while%20developing%20training%20materials%20for%20non-literate%20communities.%20She%20realised%20the%20visuals%20she%20was%20drawing%20didn%E2%80%99t%20resonate%20with%20people.%20%E2%80%9CThose%20who%20haven%E2%80%99t%20been%20to%20school%20have%20a%20completely%20different%20way%20of%20drawing.%20So%2C%20I%20created%20a%20picture%20dictionary%20on%20how%20menstruation%2C%20abortion%2C%20and%20delivery%20should%20be%20depicted.%20That%20became%20the%20basis%20for%20our%20training%20manuals%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FTBI-featured-image-2_11zon-1743597294.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FTBI-featured-image-2_11zon-1743597294.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FTBI-featured-image-2_11zon-1743597294-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FTBI-featured-image-2_11zon-1743597294-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FTBI-featured-image-2_11zon-1743597294-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FTBI-featured-image-2_11zon-1743597294-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-417521%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ELakshmi%20presents%20her%20picture%20dictionary%20%E2%80%94%20a%20visual%20tool%20she%20created%20to%20explain%20puberty%20and%20reproductive%20health%20to%20non-literate%20communities.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202000%2C%20she%20received%20the%20prestigious%20MacArthur%20Fellowship%20to%20create%20reproductive%20health%20material%20for%20rural%20adolescents%2C%20and%20in%202001%2C%20she%20co-founded%20the%20NGO%20%E2%80%98Jatan%20Sansthan%E2%80%99%20with%20Dr%20Kailash%20Brijwasi.%20Her%20focus%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F170476%2Findia-oscar-winner-period-documentary-winner%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emenstrual%20health%20%3C%2Fa%3Edeepened%20during%20this%20time%2C%20especially%20around%20the%20need%20for%20safe%2C%20sustainable%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20initially%20designed%20a%20simple%20washable%20cloth%20napkin%20%E2%80%94%20a%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Enada%20wala%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20pad%20(a%20pad%20with%20cloth%20ties%20or%20strings)%20%E2%80%94%20for%20girls%20who%20didn%E2%80%99t%20wear%20underwear.%20It%20could%20be%20stitched%20from%20old%20%3Cem%3Epetticoats%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20%3Cem%3Esaris%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20But%20when%20rural%20women%20began%20shifting%20to%20underwear%20by%20the%20late%202000s%2C%20her%20original%20design%20quietly%20faded%20away.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20first%20pad%20died%20a%20quiet%20death%20once%20women%20started%20using%20underwear.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20576px)%20100vw%2C%20576px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FA-trainer-teaching-a-young-girl-how-to-make-a-nada-wala-pad-in-2001-1743519748.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22576%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lakshmi%E2%80%99s%20first%20design%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98nada%20wala%20pad%E2%80%99%2C%20was%20made%20from%20upcycled%20cloth%20with%20ties.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-me