com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FThe-first-design-from-2000-or-the-nada-wala-pad-1743519071-150x66.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-417320%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22253%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%C2%A0%3Cem%3ELakshmi%E2%80%99s%20early%20pad%20design%20%E2%80%94%20simple%2C%20washable%2C%20biodegradable%20%E2%80%94%20was%20made%20for%20rural%20girls%20long%20before%20pads%20became%20mainstream.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20the%20same%20time%2C%20women%20in%20villages%20began%20using%20the%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Elal%20kapda%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20a%20woollen%20felt%20fabric%20which%20could%20be%20washed%20and%20reused%20for%20about%20three%20months%20until%20it%20wore%20out.%20But%20it%20was%20uncomfortable.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20very%20troubled%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Lakshmi%20searched%20for%20better%20alternatives%2C%20the%20larger%20menstrual%20health%20space%20was%20also%20shifting.%20Arunachalam%20Muruganantham%2C%20now%20widely%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98Padman%E2%80%99%2C%20began%20developing%20affordable%20disposable%20pads.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20menstrual%20cup%20%E2%80%94%20marketed%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98She%20Cup%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20was%20gaining%20attention%20in%20urban%20circles.%20But%20Lakshmi%20remained%20cautious.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20not%20very%20comfortable%20with%20the%20menstrual%20cup%20for%20my%20rural%20adolescents.%20The%20wearer%20has%20to%20learn%20how%20to%20place%20and%20wear%20it.%20If%20they%20have%20medical%20issues%2C%20there%20is%20no%20access%20to%20gynaecologists%20in%20rural%20areas.%20So%2C%20Jatan%20Sansthan%20has%20not%20promoted%20menstrual%20cups